OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FThree significant changes to ITV 1
OL,7,Fhappen on Monday. To breakfast and
OL,8,Fnews, to daytime and to the flagship
OL,9,Fsoaps.
OL,11,FSadly, they are all driven by economic
OL,12,Fnecessity ` a fall in advertising
OL,13,Flinked to declining linear audiences
OL,14,Fover the longer term.
OL,16,FThese have been difficult times for
OL,17,Fsome staff.
OL,19,FMany people who worked on Good Morning
OL,20,FBritain and the daytime shows have been
OL,21,Flet go.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15802
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe cuts to Coronation Street and
OL,7,FEmmerdale have also meant less work is
OL,8,Favailable.
OL,10,FWider challenges within TV production
OL,11,Fmean that some of those who have lost
OL,12,Ftheir jobs may find it hard to secure
OL,13,Fregular employment in television again.
OL,15,FSurveys by trade union BECTU have
OL,16,Fhighlighted the number of TV freelance
OL,17,Fworkers who do not have regular
OL,18,Femployment in the industry.
OL,20,FIt will be interesting though to see
OL,21,Fwhat impact the changes have on viewing
OL,22,Fpatterns.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15803
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn different circumstances, it would
OL,7,Fseem sensible to fully integrate Good
OL,8,FMorning Britain into the wider ITV News
OL,9,Foperation at ITN.
OL,11,FFor a long time, the overall
OL,12,Fcredibility of ITV's news service was
OL,13,Fundermined by the separate breakfast
OL,14,Foperation.
OL,16,FThe shameful coverage by TV-am of the
OL,17,FBrighton bomb in 1984 nearly caused the
OL,18,FIBA to pull the plug. Perhaps they
OL,19,Fshould have?
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15804
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FITN must have been furious on that
OL,7,Fterrible morning, left unable to
OL,8,Fprovide coverage of the attempted
OL,9,Fassassination of Margaret Thatcher and
OL,10,Fher Cabinet.
OL,12,FDid the public realise that TV-am was
OL,13,Fan entirely separate operation? Or did
OL,14,Fsome viewers wrongly assume ITV and ITN
OL,15,Fcould do no better?
OL,17,FIn more recent years, nobody would
OL,18,Fquestion the professionalism of GMTV's
OL,19,Fnews operation.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15805
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FAfter ITV took full control of GMTV in
OL,7,F2010, the news operation during
OL,8,FDaybreak and later the modern
OL,9,Fincarnation of GMB started to be
OL,10,Fproperly integrated with the rest of
OL,11,Fthe ITV News team at ITN. But the wider
OL,12,Fprogramme remained separate.
OL,14,FThere is certainly the potential for a
OL,15,Fleaner, meaner, more efficient
OL,16,Foperation. It's just a shame this is
OL,17,Fhappening amid wider cuts and job
OL,18,Flosses.
OL,20,FThe cosmetic changes to GMB and ITV
OL,21,FNews should be interesting.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15806
SC,0006
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FAt this point it is unclear whether the
OL,7,Fon-screen changes will be evolutionary
OL,8,For lead to obvious changes in the
OL,9,Fprogrammes.
OL,11,FThe cuts to the rest of daytime though
OL,12,Fare much more depressing.
OL,14,FEssentially ` make no mistake ` this is
OL,15,Fabout cutting the cost of Lorraine,
OL,16,FThis Morning and Loose Women.
OL,18,FIf the ratings can be maintained on
OL,19,Flower budgets, the production teams
OL,20,Fwill have worked wonders.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15807
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FI cannot help but wonder if Lorraine's
OL,7,Fprogramme will be dropped in the next
OL,8,Fyear or two. And what will replace
OL,9,FLoose Women while it is off for half
OL,10,Fthe year? A new programme? Or a repeat
OL,11,Fof Tenable?
OL,13,FI have slightly mixed feelings about
OL,14,Fthe changes to evening soaps. While the
OL,15,Fjob cuts are a matter of regret, might
OL,16,Fless mean more?
OL,18,FThe exponential expansion of the main
OL,19,Fsoaps in recent years has almost
OL,20,Fcertainly been a false economy.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15808
SC,0008
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe initial ratings justified the extra
OL,7,Fepisodes. But in the longer term, did
OL,8,Fviewer fatigue set in? Storylines were
OL,9,Fgobbled up quickly. And were those
OL,10,Fviewers who could not commit to
OL,11,Fwatching quite so many episodes left
OL,12,Fcold?
OL,14,FIt will be worth keeping an eye on
OL,15,FEmmerdale and Coronation Street's
OL,16,Fratings. Might they actually improve in
OL,17,Fthe coming months?
OL,19,FNote too the end of regular direct
OL,20,Fclashes between the two big ITV soaps
OL,21,Fand EastEnders. This could be win-win.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,159,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15809
SC,0009
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F158A1773864688
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G9/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV daytime, news and soap
OL,4,Cchanges
OL,5,
OL,6,FHaving said all that, the ITV soap hour
OL,7,Fis likely to be thumped in the ratings
OL,8,Fon Thursdays and Fridays for the next
OL,9,Ffew weeks by The Traitors.
OL,11,FSo, Monday and next week will prove
OL,12,Fvery interesting. And so too will the
OL,13,Fcoming months.
OL,15,FBut it must not be forgotten that these
OL,16,Fchanges are cuts and for some TV
OL,17,Fworkers recent months have been
OL,18,Fpainful.
OL,23,EPub: 04-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
